Content:
bash has functions; functions are just like commands. Write your comments in the functions, and your final line will be the pipeline of awesomeness:<p><pre><code>   generate_data ()
       {
        # make it rain
       }

   process ()
       {
        # chunky
       }

   gather ()
       {
        # puree
       }

   generate_data | process | gather</code></pre>
